OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day for most, with sunny
OL,6,Fspells, but isolated afternoon showers
OL,7,Fare possible in one or two spots.
OL,8,FTemperatures cooler than yesterday
OL,9,Finland, perhaps a little warmer near
OL,10,Fcoasts, but rather breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry night with clear
OL,13,Fspells, and overnight temperatures a
OL,14,Flittle fresher than of late especially
OL,15,Fin rural spots. Wind easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
